MatchedObjectDescriptor.QualificationSummary:
Your resume must demonstrate at least one year of specialized experience at or equivalent to the GS-12 grade level or pay band in the Federal service or equivalent experience in the private or public sector. Specialized experience must demonstrate the following:
1) Developing, maintaining, and updating Naval Aviation Technical Publication in IETMS (S1000D) format, manipulating data from raw source data to published digital technical publications;
2) Communicating both orally and in writing to effectively lead and collaborate with a team of at least 5 technical data managers or more;
3) Conducting research on the availability and funds, materials, and time restrictions to successfully negotiate contracts and project requirements to achieve a mutually desired outcome;
4) Assessing the abilities of the department to meet current, future, and contingency requirements and developing plans and programs to enhance capabilities and performance while maintaining cost as an independent variable;
5) Providing necessary training and technical guidance to prepare individuals to successfully support logistics support programs. Additional qualification information can be found from the following Office of Personnel Management web site: https://www.opm.gov/policy-data-oversight/classification-qualifications/general-schedule-qualification-standards/#url=List-by-Occupational-Series Experience refers to paid and unpaid experience, including volunteer work done through National Service programs (e.g., professional, philanthropic, religious, spiritual, community, student, social). Volunteer work helps build critical competencies, knowledge, and skills and can provide valuable training and experience that translates directly to paid employment.

Details.Education:
Education may be substituted for specialized experience as follows:
A Ph.D. or equivalent doctoral degree;
OR
Three full years of progressively higher level graduate education leading to a Ph.D. or equivalent degree;
OR
An LL.M. degree in a field directly related to the position being filled;
OR
A combination of experience and graduate education as described above that equates to one year of experience.
